column3: I would like contributing a few small changes to enhance your great product.
This is my first time sending a pull request to an open source project and the first time using GitHub & Git so please give me a hint if I do something wrong.
I signed the contribution agreement a few weeks ago and sent it by post, but I didn¡¯t receive any acknowledgement.
Merged manually. Thanks for your contribution Josef!
Thanks Dmitry for reviewing my patches. I will send you a few additional pull requests in the near future.
